title: Lynyrd_Skynyrd_shows
description:
Includes...

Full Shows: 
April 1975 - Winterland Ballroom, San Francisco (with Ed King and in black and white)
March 1976 - Winterland Ballroom, San Francisco (with "only" two guitarists and in black and white)
August 1976 - Knebworth Festival, England (has audio/video sync issues)
July 1977 - Convention Hall, Asbury Park, NJ (with Steve Gaines and in black and white)

Also has:

Full 1975 appearance on England's "Old Grey Whistle Test" television show (with "only" two guitarists)
VH1's Behind the Music
"Skynyrd Uncivil War" from VH1 (sleazy, tabloid-style piece from 2002)
All 82 minutes of live clips from "Freebird: The Movie," which includes most of the 1976 Knebworth Festival set without audio problems
